{"tid":1392340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警告!8月5日千祈唔好再做呢樣野","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T17:52:32.000Z","uid":283912,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca704de06432a0e0776c91c5a51371c7f803f109","tid":1392340,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"就係地鐵不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地係咪唔記得雨革點解唔work?擾民阿<br />\n你越搞政府越開心,完全係送子彈,輿論送頭<br />\n你地可以屌人掛住返工係港豬係垃圾<br />\n但事實係香港人未衝破到返工呢件事<br />\n我地依家要爭贏唔係同返工港豬爭對錯<br />\n而呢件事我可以話你知100%唔work仲有機搞散個運動<br />\n8月5要罷嘅自己會罷,我地可以做嘅就係文宣同文宣<br />\n你塞地鐵迫人罷政府一定吹大風叫哂受影響不滿嘅人黎反我地<br />\n到時請問你地爭到d咩?<br />\n<br />\n明嘅話同我去文宣,唔認同嘅我擺低老母俾你屌"},{"pid":"992db58511f06f6d22dd8b4b41664736ee58c63a","tid":1392340,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0612e6f55e5fb049fb3ce1aa9c726c6f4722f4c5","tid":1392340,"uid":119897,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:11:05.000Z","msg":"上次唔係輸擾民 <br />\n<br />\n係唔夠擾民"},{"pid":"84e35df23452bd0ca02d5abe794fa37cf9fad8f3","tid":1392340,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:11:25.000Z","msg":"［理性討論］有冇人答到我點解要塞地鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21426c2e599347a502cb33ee1c10686cbe8084d2","tid":1392340,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0612e6f55e5fb049fb3ce1aa9c726c6f4722f4c5","tid":1392340,"uid":119897,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:11:05.000Z","msg":"上次唔係輸擾民 <br />\n<br />\n係唔夠擾民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"一定要塞 塞佢老母 塞夠一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ac47798e9c05551c1d85e238f3d1a7083ff5a2","tid":1392340,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07